OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,6,FGenerally dry with variable cloud for
OL,7,FTuesday and Wednesday, though
OL,8,Ftemperatures may start to reduce from
OL,9,FTuesday as the wind turns onshore.
OL,10,FCloudier with showers possible on
OL,11,FThursday.
